{"tid":416661,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[創業撚]地區選擇點揀好","createTime":"2017-09-28T03:00:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-03T09:19:02.000Z","uid":32782,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"82345347424da1fd6a91db8d84bb32666a6011c4","tid":416661,"uid":32782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T03:00:58.000Z","msg":"同朋友傾緊創業，打算做飲食方面<br />\n想問下你地會揀邊個地方去做<br />\n我就主張深圳，朋友就主張台中，台北同退而求其次上海<br />\n<br />\n我認為深圳嗰邊近香港，口味同飲食習慣相若，感覺相對穩定<br />\n而佢就打算賣特色所以想去台灣(台中&gt;台北)，主要做旅客生意<br />\n<br />\n各位點睇？"},{"pid":"a57fe333302a98244f3a1a98f452521d205eb62f","tid":416661,"uid":32782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T03:05:56.000Z","msg":"Btw朋友仲覺得深圳好窮，幾蚊雞d食物都要諗過度過。上次帶佢去深圳睇d人排哂大隊買杯RMB 20up嘅喜茶佢依然唔相信呢個事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1ed23bd8a2e3fb9631da06b5c9db1a970862e3a","tid":416661,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T03:09:14.000Z","msg":"台灣做&ldquo;香港特色&rdquo; 唔睇好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5e83ea914755277f3a58b0d413848e0ca9a68d8","tid":416661,"uid":32782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T03:25:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>台灣做&ldquo;香港特色&rdquo; 唔睇好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打可唔可以講下你睇法？<br />\n<br />\n我朋友因為之前係係台灣讀過書，而佢亦有所謂嘅&quot;人脈&quot;<br />\n之後我隨便google過三個地方嘅數據，無論收入，人口數量，消費力都係深圳行先，之後台北最後台中。但佢依然堅持要去台中做開荒牛<br />\n<br />\n仲有就係上次睇過兩三個深圳商場，佢下下拎新城市廣場d人口密度來比，然後一口斷定深圳無得做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dedb5cee49a79e4a390175055e1b7c5beb2ce22a","tid":416661,"uid":32782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T04:13:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38540a107f2bf2dad35635e283b8e2cbc1909e1e","tid":416661,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T04:15:14.000Z","msg":"做銅鑼灣最旺嗰條街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee0dc5efb5066dee2ac44c6c7ef5e3d31f5de64f","tid":416661,"uid":32782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T04:26:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做銅鑼灣最旺嗰條街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n資金一個月租都比唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaf511dee354c9ba22ac38bf7591c4a741586175","tid":416661,"uid":32782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T05:00:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85d9164d4321d89f88f561edbe228a2114dc1893","tid":416661,"uid":32782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T05:56:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66fe820b38dda7bc979b07af9429ee1afe8d3d1a","tid":416661,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T05:58:13.000Z","msg":"係煩在唔知拎乜飲食牌?"},{"pid":"7414cc867995b64d62cbeb32fcc6596a55f91fc1","tid":416661,"uid":133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T06:00:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Btw朋友仲覺得深圳好窮，幾蚊雞d食物都要諗過度過。上次帶佢去深圳睇d人排哂大隊買杯RMB 20up嘅喜茶佢依然唔相信呢個事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n深圳就快收皮啦, 表面風光姐."},{"pid":"408e3d61be08ea82fbd5eb9626edf46bf60fc229","tid":416661,"uid":32782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T06:33:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係煩在唔知拎乜飲食牌?</blockquote><br />\n呢個問題不太<br />\n係嘈傾邊個地方做生意容易d<br />\n我覺得我地做嗰d野台仔唔會點食"},{"pid":"5ee6c2d91c9929351a04249b2b94365fafbd4f2d","tid":416661,"uid":32782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T06:35:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Btw朋友仲覺得深圳好窮，幾蚊雞d食物都要諗過度過。上次帶佢去深圳睇d人排哂大隊買杯RMB 20up嘅喜茶佢依然唔相信呢個事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" cla